AB  - [Purpose/significance] At present, the key areas of national defense science and technology are crucial to national security and military game. The research on the construction of intelligence analysis model for the development situation of key areas of national defense science and technology is helpful for intelligence researchers to make use of the logical advantages of the model to conduct a comprehensive analysis of the development situation of key areas of national defense science and technology and form intelligence cognition. [Method/process] Based on the systematic investigation of the current research status of intelligence analysis models and the task requirements of developing situational intelligence analysis in key areas of national defense science and technology, this study draws on Endsley’s situational awareness theory to build a situational intelligence analysis model of developing situational intelligence in key areas of national defense science and technology, which is composed of four levels: information collection layer, situation awareness layer, situation understanding layer and situation prediction layer. [Result/conclusion] The development situation intelligence analysis model of the key areas of national defense science and technology has a wide range of applicability, and provides a technical route and method with strong operability for the development situation analysis of the key areas of national defense science and technology such as artificial intelligence, quantum science and biotechnology.
